2# Installation instructions

1. Install flymake for emacs.

2. Install modified csharp-mode into emacs
--- Option 1: Load the files from the folder here in your .emacs file
--- Option 2: Install stock csharp-mode via elpa (M-x package-install csharp-mode),
              and then replace ~/.emacs.d/elpa/csharp-mode-0.8.6/ with the folder here

3. Replace hardcoded paths in csharp-mode.el and stylecheck
--- Search for "/home/nikita/"

4. Add stylecheck to the PATH

5. Restart emacs